- `src/config/model-tools.ts` â€” **start here for model-specific behavior**. Per-model caps with glob matching.
- `src/config/constants.ts` â€” `SUPPORTED_MODELS`, `TOKEN_LIMITS`
- `src/config/toml-config.ts` â€” config profiles (`[profiles.<name>]` deep-merged; `buddy --profile <name>`). Also `[model_pairs]` for architect/editor split.
- `src/config/advanced-config.ts` â€” effort levels (low/medium/high) â†’ temperature + token params

## Coding Conventions

- TypeScript strict, avoid `any`
- Single quotes, semicolons, 2-space indent
- Files kebab-case (`text-editor.ts`); React components PascalCase (`ChatInterface.tsx`)
- Conventional Commits (`feat(scope): description`)
