## Special Modes

- **YOLO** â€” 400 tool rounds, $100 cap, auto-approve with guardrails. `src/utils/autonomy-manager.ts`. `/yolo on|off|safe|status|allow|deny`.
- **Agent modes** â€” `plan`, `code`, `ask`, `architect` â€” each restricts available tools.
- **Permission modes** â€” `default`, `plan`, `acceptEdits`, `dontAsk`, `bypassPermissions`. CLI: `--permission-mode <mode>`. Checked by `ConfirmationService` before every approval. `src/security/permission-modes.ts`.
- **Security modes** â€” `suggest` / `auto-edit` / `full-auto`.
- **Write policy** â€” `strict` (forces `apply_patch`) / `confirm` / `off`. `src/security/write-policy.ts`.
- **Plan mode** â€” `/plan` enters read-only research mode; write tools restricted to `.md` plan files.

